    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049240/extras/96a2981bff1c8c0600ab9d37e48a937e.avif?t=1770215682\" width=768 height=622 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spaceborn: Awakening是一款<i>叙事驱动的roguelite弹幕天堂</i>，你将扮演一支传奇太空船员，回应来自星系边缘幽灵般太空站的神秘求救信号。消灭Voss Praetor腐化军队的大军，觉醒你的真正潜能，了解第一个Spaceborn的真相，并对抗将决定宇宙命运的星际力量。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049240/extras/6d85c8ca9740d1ec380f47daebf4dbc5.avif?t=1770215682\" width=512 height=136 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049240/extras/5b08e7d58169ffe856362526b7145eb1.poster.avif?t=1770215682\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049240/extras/5b08e7d58169ffe856362526b7145eb1.webm?t=1770215682\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049240/extras/5b08e7d58169ffe856362526b7145eb1.mp4?t=1770215682\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >杀穿敌人的波次，揭露禁忌实验，面对虚空的腐化。解锁强大武器，掌握你觉醒的Spaceborn能力，尽可能长时间地生存下去。在虚空吞噬你之前，你敢深入多远？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049240/extras/7da748f8d8e4d861ee119d2a8079012c.avif?t=1770215682\" width=512 height=136 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049240/extras/ec8d0c3db753f6697c6cb64e0579d171.poster.avif?t=1770215682\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049240/extras/ec8d0c3db753f6697c6cb64e0579d171.webm?t=1770215682\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049240/extras/ec8d0c3db753f6697c6cb64e0579d171.mp4?t=1770215682\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索所有故事章节以觉醒你的真正潜能。完成故事模式战役将解锁每个职业的完整「觉醒」潜能，开放高级能力和扩展的游戏风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不可预测的力量提升意味着没有两次觉醒会完全相同，而永久解锁和故事碎片将帮助玩家拼凑成为Spaceborn的真正力量——以及他们在途中觉醒的力量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049240/extras/81aa5cbcf126833491d6d90bdab42d06.avif?t=1770215682\" width=525 height=136 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049240/extras/3bbad5d4d064772686fcf33aa54b9337.poster.avif?t=1770215682\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049240/extras/3bbad5d4d064772686fcf33aa54b9337.webm?t=1770215682\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049240/extras/3bbad5d4d064772686fcf33aa54b9337.mp4?t=1770215682\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >获得庞大武器库的访问权限，并具有进化到更大潜能的能力。发现原型科技武器或深入神秘领域，解锁宇宙力量来消灭你的敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049240/extras/67cf3c631ba77dbe0534b3a72c29c183.avif?t=1770215682\" width=768 height=638 /></span></p>",
